fix: CI build/test failures + performance and security improvements

CI: fix Dockerfile prisma path, use db push instead of migrate deploy,
add vitest --run flag, add JWT_REFRESH_SECRET to test env.

Perf: batch N+1 in sendingEngine (skipped leads + message creation),
batch N+1 in autoTagService.tagColdLeads, cache isTestMode in Redis.

Security: settings key whitelist, input validation, rate limiting,
replace any types with proper AuthRequest/Response.

Stability: fix automationWorker process.exit(0) killing main server,
Redis exponential backoff reconnection, proper logger usage.

Other: pipeline pagination, tag cascade delete, pagination bounds.
